---
title: Spanish-Inspired Burger with 'Patatas Bravas' and Romesco Aioli
description: This meal is inspired by the flavours of Spain's popular tapas culture. Flavourful and slightly smoky beef burgers are topped with white cheddar, roasted red peppers and a zippy, romesco-inspired sauce. 'Patatas bravas' inspired potatoes are served alongside to complete a dish that is 'muy deliciosa!'
